{"arkId":"cl010167793","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010167793","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"tablette","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"tablette"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : Bronze r\u00e9cent II (Nouvel Empire : Am\u00e9nophis IV-Akh\u00e9naton (1353 - 1337 avant J.-C.)) (-1400 - -1200)","currentLocation":"Sully, [AO] Salle 301 - Levant - Syrie c\u00f4ti\u00e8re, Ougarit et Byblos, des origines \u00e0 l\u0027\u00e2ge du fer, Vitrine 1 Byblos : tombes royales","room":"Salle 301, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 0","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":-1400,"endYear":-1200,"imprecision":"","text":"Bronze r\u00e9cent II","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"AO 7093","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"T.2173","type":"Num\u00e9ro catalogue"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"D\u00e9cor : inscription\r\nPr\u00e9cision sur l\u0027objet : Tablette : lettre d\u0027Amarna","inscriptions":"\u00c9criture : \r ; cun\u00e9iforme\r ; syllabique\r ; Inscription : \r ; Lettre de Rib Addi, roi de Byblos, au pharaon d\u0027Egypte : \u0022 Rib Addi au roi mon seigneur : sous les pieds de mon seigneur sept et sept fois je me suis jet\u00e9. Si le pharaon n\u0027envoie pas des troupes, nous sommes morts et la ville de Gubla (Byblos) est prise. Aujourd\u0027hui comme hier et avant-hier, elle est dans l\u0027angoisse. Ses ennemis \u00e9crivent au roi \u00ab la mort (la peste) est dans le pays \u00bb mais leurs propos sont mensongers. Que le roi mon seigneur n\u0027\u00e9coute pas les paroles des autres. Il n\u0027y a pas de peste dans le pays : l\u0027\u00e9tat sanitaire y est meilleur qu\u0027auparavant.#Il essaye ensuite de flatter le roi : Vois, le jour o\u00f9 tu te mettras en route, tout le pays se ralliera au roi mon seigneur. Qui peut r\u00e9sister aux soldats du roi ?\u0022\r ; Langue : \r ; akkadien\r ; Nature du texte : \r ; lettre diplomatique","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"12,5","displayDimension":"12,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"7,5","displayDimension":"7,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argile\r\nTechnique : incis\u00e9","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"Amarna = Tell el Amarna","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Chaulais","note":"","role":""}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1918","startYear":1918,"endYear":1918}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"achat"}],"denomination":[{"value":"tablette"}],"material":[{"value":"argile"}],"technic":[{"value":"incis\u00e9"}],"description":[{"value":"inscription"}],"inscriptionLanguage":[{"value":"akkadien"}],"place":[{"value":"Amarna = Tell el Amarna"}],"inscriptionType":[{"value":"lettre diplomatique"}],"inscriptionWritingSystem":[{"value":"syllabique"},{"value":"cun\u00e9iforme"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Fontan, Elisabeth ; Le Meaux, H\u00e9l\u00e8ne (dir.), La M\u00e9diterran\u00e9e des Ph\u00e9niciens de Tyr \u00e0 Carthage, cat. exp. (Institut du monde arabe \/ 6 novembre 2007 - 20 avril 2008), Paris, Somogy \/ Institut du monde Arabe, 2007","bibliographyDate":"2007","bibliographyDetail":"p. 300, n\u00b0 9","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Moran, William Lambert, Les lettres d\u0027El-Amarna. Litt\u00e9ratu